{"tid":820034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風山竹】港珠澳大橋難抵強風？　路政署：本周初已做預防措施","createTime":"2018-09-15T08:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:16:53.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"daef620cc204d2811fb18c54a8736d15d4de47f3","tid":820034,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1864797/org/896a25c3dac431dd2d23966096e80f13.jpg/B9GRu0XH3gCiikWFSjC01bW8NgTXyAQ1eZKQ6nmSkOo?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1864797%2Forg%2F896a25c3dac431dd2d23966096e80f13.jpg%2FB9GRu0XH3gCiikWFSjC01bW8NgTXyAQ1eZKQ6nmSkOo%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=634edb83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n超強颱風「山竹」即將於周末殺到本港！政府今午（14日）舉行跨部門記者會，交待應對措施。各方關注港珠澳大橋只能預防16級颱風，或未能抵受達17級的「山竹」，路政署在會上指，大橋設計採取相當高的標準、安全系數亦較大，故有足夠能力抗風。<br />\n<br />\n路政署於傍晚再回覆傳媒時表示，本周初起，署方已聯同駐地盤工程人員及各承建商，為大橋香港段工程進行徹底巡查，和成立緊急事故應變小組，並監督完成相颱風預防措施，包括大樓玻璃幕墻及門窗的加固及關合、疏導排水系統暢順，及準備足夠的臨時抽水泵等。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1861967/org/0df03ef31bca33e5d60dc120d3627c75.jpg/51utLK1pz-ccxP3zh5JV1JG9_zUaQUo9i7-q8Iu_qvA?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1861967%2Forg%2F0df03ef31bca33e5d60dc120d3627c75.jpg%2F51utLK1pz-ccxP3zh5JV1JG9_zUaQUo9i7-q8Iu_qvA%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=d0760f6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前有指港珠澳大橋可抵抗16級颱風，惟超強颱風「山竹」的風力達到17級</span>，引起不少人擔心大橋或未能承受強勁風力，而有倒塌的危險。路政署表示，本周初開始，署方已聯同駐地盤工程人員及各承建商，為大橋香港段工程進行徹底巡查，並監督各承建商完成相關颱風預防措施。 <br />\n<br />\n署方指，各承建商正加緊做各項防風措施，包括完成旅檢大樓和輔助建築物的玻璃幕牆，及門窗的加固及關合；卸下工程機械吊臂；安排工程船隻停泊到鄰近的避風塘；繫緊容易被大風吹倒的建築物料；穩固臨時工作台及棚架；疏導及確保建築物屋頂、及道路的排水系統暢順；在低窪處入口放置砂包防止雨水灌入；準備足夠的臨時抽水泵，方便有需要時抽走積水；移走有機會被吹倒的樹枝和樹幹等。<br />\n<br />\n此外，路政署、駐地盤工程人員及各承建商的工程團隊，已成立緊急事故應變小組，於風暴期間作出有效指揮，及跟進有關緊急應變措施，並在颱風過後檢視各設施的情況。署方指，會密切監察情况，確保公眾、工人及工地安全。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/235682/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F235682%2F&d=LAMxYje7rJLtKWYjQiVkEtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8448cb10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/235682/</a>"},{"pid":"cb92c7070cd428ba62b5c3d75d7323bdc58148ea","tid":820034,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"我地D千億基建點算,好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efeec771abac2e58705b4a93157fa11e01c417a","tid":820034,"uid":1069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:04:29.000Z","msg":"都係冇答到17級風問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b99e7ca13752c232a8c948606f7651727e50171","tid":820034,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb92c7070cd428ba62b5c3d75d7323bdc58148ea","tid":820034,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"我地D千億基建點算,好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"起過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a156ffbaa0b4457941bd0f3e2dbd5790cf7802","tid":820034,"uid":116688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"成個島都隨機機擺放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5e9013e487348ce84ae527ba0eae2fe1055d61","tid":820034,"uid":179645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:08:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">哦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8051df781d2d884d397dd39bb1336c9fdaa3a3","tid":820034,"uid":109173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"起多次又CAP幾百億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree